sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant UI as React Dashboard
  participant API as Fastify REST routes
  participant RT as Socket.IO gateway/handlers
  participant Guard as TelemetryIngressGuard
  participant Dev as DeviceService
  participant Tel as TelemetryService
  participant Spec as SpectrumStorageService
  participant Cmd as CommandService
  participant DB as MySQL + in-memory repos
  participant Edge as Sensor Device

  UI->>API: Fetch zones, devices, history, OTA screens
  API->>DB: Query/update domain state
  DB-->>API: Records and summaries
  API-->>UI: JSON response

  Edge->>RT: device:heartbeat / device:metadata
  RT->>Dev: upsert device state
  RT-->>UI: device:heartbeat / device:metadata

  Edge->>RT: device:telemetry
  RT->>Guard: validate/rate-limit ingress
  Guard-->>RT: accepted sample
  RT->>Tel: persist sample + enrich device context
  Tel->>DB: write telemetry
  Tel-->>RT: latest telemetry view
  RT-->>UI: telemetry

  UI->>API: Create command / OTA action
  API->>Cmd: plan or enqueue command
  Cmd->>DB: save command state
  Cmd->>RT: send device:command
  RT-->>Edge: device:command
  Edge-->>RT: device:command:ack
  RT->>Cmd: update command status
  RT-->>UI: device:ack / device:command
